    dc:title="Voting should be made compulsary"
    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/1277"
    dc:description="Voting should be made compulsary so long as they add a "None of the above" section to the voting form. That will prove once and for all that we are not abstaining because we're lazy, we're abstaining because we ..."
